1
00:00:03,636 --> 00:00:04,636
Good morning.

2
00:00:17,083 --> 00:00:19,085
Weren't you sleeping

3
00:00:19,719 --> 00:00:21,054
over there last night?

4
00:00:24,791 --> 00:00:26,226
Who knows?

5
00:00:26,393 --> 00:00:27,927
You must've been freezing

6
00:00:28,795 --> 00:00:30,063
and used me as a blanket.

7
00:00:31,664 --> 00:00:33,633
I've always run hot,

8
00:00:34,300 --> 00:00:35,101
so my classmates used to

9
00:00:35,102 --> 00:00:36,402
shove their hands in my shirt

10
00:00:36,403 --> 00:00:37,403
to stay warm.

11
00:00:37,504 --> 00:00:38,772
I'm actually a bit cold now.

12
00:00:39,339 --> 00:00:40,507
- Hey!
- Warm me up.

13
00:00:43,777 --> 00:00:46,679
You... really love sleeping in.

14
00:00:47,414 --> 00:00:48,915
I bet you're always late.

15
00:00:49,616 --> 00:00:51,851
I usually wake up an hour early.

16
00:00:54,154 --> 00:00:55,321
Just five more minutes...

17
00:00:59,959 --> 00:01:01,694
Get up already!

18
00:01:08,635 --> 00:01:10,503
Why are you still on your phone?

19
00:01:15,442 --> 00:01:18,178
At least your fever's gone.

20
00:01:19,946 --> 00:01:22,582
But those dark circles are still bad.

21
00:01:26,519 --> 00:01:28,621
We need to fix this,

22
00:01:29,022 --> 00:01:30,423
or we can't sleep together anymore.

23
00:01:31,124 --> 00:01:32,124
Why not?

24
00:01:32,625 --> 00:01:34,394
Because I won't get any rest.

25
00:01:35,295 --> 00:01:36,295
Why?

26
00:01:36,629 --> 00:01:39,265
Because I'd be watching you all night.

27
00:01:39,899 --> 00:01:40,899
Why?

28
00:01:42,001 --> 00:01:43,702
Because you talk in your sleep,

29
00:01:43,703 --> 00:01:45,003
and you kept hugging me

30
00:01:45,004 --> 00:01:46,004
like a giant teddy bear.

31
00:01:46,005 --> 00:01:47,239
Plus, you're a restless sleeper.

32
00:01:47,240 --> 00:01:48,400
You kept tossing and turning.

33
00:01:52,412 --> 00:01:53,980
You even took a picture?

34
00:01:55,548 --> 00:01:56,548
It's evidence.

35
00:01:58,885 --> 00:02:00,286
Why didn't you just push me away?

36
00:02:01,287 --> 00:02:02,522
I was taking one for the team.

37
00:02:02,722 --> 00:02:03,755
If the footage ever leaked,

38
00:02:03,756 --> 00:02:04,836
it'd be bad for your image.

39
00:02:05,725 --> 00:02:06,693
Wait a second...

40
00:02:06,693 --> 00:02:07,560
Why are we

41
00:02:07,561 --> 00:02:08,761
sleeping together from now on?
